data.description: Nestled in the heart of the beautiful Santee community, this updated two-story pool home is a true gem that combines modern comforts with the natural beauty. With close proximity to the lakes, you'll have easy access to recreational opportunities, hiking trails, and serene lakeside views. With its charming curb appeal and well-manicured front yard this home is sure to make a lasting first impression.  Features include central AC, a separate upstairs family room with a cozy fireplace, and durable flooring throughout the main living areas of the home.  A beautifully appointed kitchen featuring warm honey-hued cabinetry.  All of the bedrooms are on the main floor including the spacious primary suite offering ample closet space and its own en-suite bathroom.  Outdoor living has been extended to the spacious backyard featuring thoughtfully designed hardscape including a sparkling pool, covered patio, and low maintenance landscaping, making it perfect for entertaining and taking in the gorgeous views.  Conveniently located near shopping centers, restaurants, Mission trails, and top-rated schools. It offers easy access to major freeways for a quick commute to San Diego and other nearby destinations. Don’t miss out!
